title: CAT 320 Excavator - 500 Hour Service
description: Engine oil and filter change. Hydraulic filter replacement. Undercarriage inspection and track tension adjustment. Greased all pivot points. Checked coolant level and condition.

title: Liebherr LTM 1060 Crane - Annual Inspection
description: Annual OSHA/ANSI crane inspection. Load test at 100% and 125% capacity. Wire rope inspection - no defects found. All safety devices functional. Boom condition satisfactory. Certification renewed.

title: Generac 100kW Generator - Fuel System Repair
description: Fuel injector replacement on cylinders 2 and 4 due to rough running and black smoke. Replaced fuel filters. Tested under load for 2 hours - running smooth. Checked transfer switch operation.

title: Genie GS-2632 Scissor Lift - Hydraulic Leak
description: Hydraulic cylinder seal replacement on main lift cylinder. Flushed hydraulic system and refilled with new fluid. Function tested all controls. Platform leveling checked.

title: John Deere 310SL Backhoe - 250 Hour Service
description: Engine oil and filter change. Transmission fluid check. Air filter replacement. Battery terminals cleaned. Bucket teeth inspected - 2 replaced due to wear. Tire pressure adjusted.

title: Ford F-350 Service Truck - Brake Replacement
description: Front and rear brake pad replacement. Rotors resurfaced. Brake fluid flush. Parking brake adjustment. Road test completed satisfactory.
